---
title: Seared Steak with Demi Reduction served with Garlic Mashed Potatoes & Honey-Roasted Carrots
description: Hankering for a plate of good ol’ steak and potatoes? We’ve got what you need and then some! Yep, our chefs have officially perfected the classic pairing. There’s creamy garlic mashed potatoes, roasted carrots tossed with honey, and perfectly seared steak (of course). And on top? Beef demi-glace, scallions, and sour cream mingle to create a rich and savory elixir you’ll want to drizzle over everything. And now you can!
